<br>
Bau, waitt is cool and all but when it comes down to it its not that great for the prices people try to sell for, I think the prices in auction are all based on hype.  Same with freedom arms, there is pistols out there that are actully better just not as common and people think they are crap... why? because of the hype, they really dont know.<br>
<br>
I was gona buy some armor after I did all my token runs and saw the prices and was like uh.. pleeeze I dont think so.  Went to the mission machine and what did I end up getting? A full set of bau for FREE in 2.5 hours.. at level 16.<br>
<br>
Try to get missions that are the eye over a box when trying for specific items, that way you can get a extra chance on getting that item.  Also if thats not working you can do the retreive item missions but just not finish them and keep the item instead of returning it.  Hell you could get a bau helm at level 20 easy on a mission and turn right around and sell it on auction then use the money to buy 2-3 peices of other armor same ql like ma or kevlar to have a smooth black look,  think about it, 20 points of armor seems like a lot at level 15-20 but thats only -2 damage a hit.  <p>Keidric<BR>

